      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5415 - Abdullah ibn Al-Mughirah narrated from Al-Sakuni from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), who said:\n\"Whoever does not make a will for his relatives at the time of his death has concluded his deeds with disobedience.\""
